}}'''Ruffle'''是一款用于播放[[Swf|Swf]]文件的[[开源|开源]][[媒体播放器|媒体播放器]]。它的开发者将其描述为一个「Flash Player模拟器」。Ruffle是用[[Rust|Rust]]编写，适用于桌面端和網頁端。
== 歷史 ==
2016年，迈克·威尔士（Mike Welsh）開啟一个名为Fluster的项目。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Initial commit · ruffle-rs/ruffle@b979ac2|url=https://github.com/ruffle-rs/ruffle/commit/b979ac26a9dad77ca66c3f9171efac4acfa8c19d|access-date=2020-07-24|website=GitHub|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110163246/https://github.com/ruffle-rs/ruffle/commit/b979ac26a9dad77ca66c3f9171efac4acfa8c19d}}</ref>后来改名为Ruffle。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Update README · ruffle-rs/ruffle@0d9d5fe|url=https://github.com/ruffle-rs/ruffle/commit/0d9d5fe57d29fea3b829bc81fc3e97d1916df6f0#diff-04c6e90faac2675aa89e2176d2eec7d8|access-date=2020-07-24|website=GitHub|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211110033012/https://github.com/ruffle-rs/ruffle/commit/0d9d5fe57d29fea3b829bc81fc3e97d1916df6f0#diff-04c6e90faac2675aa89e2176d2eec7d8}}</ref>

由於[[Adobe_Flash_Player|Adobe Flash Player]]逐步關閉，2019年至2020年之间，一些网站宣布将啟用Ruffle。例如[[Newgrounds|Newgrounds]]就宣布，所有的Flash嵌入代码将被替换成Ruffle。<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Flash Emulation & Brave BAT|url=https://www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/1444275|access-date=2021-02-07|website=Newgrounds.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210427223516/https://www.newgrounds.com/bbs/topic/1444275}}</ref>

